description: Artemis Gold Inc., a gold development company, focuses on the identification, acquisition, and development of gold properties. The company's asset portfolio includes a 32.3% equity interests in Velocity Minerals Ltd. that focuses on acquiring, exploring, and evaluating mineral resource properties in Bulgaria. It also holds interest in the Blackwater Gold Project located in central British Columbia. Artemis Gold Inc. was incorporated in 2019 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Steven Graham Dean A.U.S.I.M.M., C.I.M., F.C.A.
